data.description: This stunning home boasts a sleek open floor plan, modern concrete floors, and a captivating kitchen featuring a spacious island, and luxurious granite countertops.  With an oversized garage and meticulous maintenance, it offers a NEW roof, NEW HVAC outside unit, and NEW exterior maintenance free siding for worry free living. An added gem is the detached Man-cave, fully equipped with heating and cooling, and a built-in bar perfect for private retreats or entertaining friends. Use this space for hobbies, music, or anything imaginable that requires a little extra space. A storage shed is also included to give extra storage. The homes curbside appeal is simply enchanting, setting the tone for its remarkable interior.  From the beauty of the beautifully maintained exterior to the inviting atmosphere, this house is a delight from the moment you arrive. Schedule a showing with the agent today!
